reviewText: A total waste of money!!!! Very poor quality production. Loved the theme because it reminded me of watching these types of movies as a kid.....but the quality really is bad.

The dvd worked fine but the picture quality was poor. I am sure that this was beyond the control of the seller and I would rather have a poor copy than no copy.
Please don't take this as a criticism of the seller.
I, Think that Amazon.com,shouldn't sell, this kind of videos, your quality is the worst that I see in my life.

It is too bad film. Old, old screen .

I disapoint very much. I think don't sale this dvd.
